Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.97,SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs72\pos(365,372)}Execution
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.47,0:00:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to continue disposing of criminals in this manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.01,0:00:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once this is over, you can do whatever you want with this notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.19,0:00:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.65,0:00:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If everything goes according to Yagami Light's plan, this should save Misa...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.46,0:00:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a good deal for both you and me, don't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.26,0:00:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you might say, "it's good business", right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.72,0:00:39.35,MINOR SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\fscx113.75\fscy98.75\pos(358,391)}Imprisonment: Day Fifty
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.73,0:00:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-san, you okay there?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.33,0:00:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, there's no need for you to continue doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.86,0:00:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been more than a month since criminals began to be killed by Kira again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.56,0:00:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm convinced my son is not Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.23,0:00:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now all that remains, Ryuuzaki, is for you to realize this too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.57,0:01:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I leave here, it will be with my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.00,0:01:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Chief is so stubborn...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.25,0:01:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.96,0:01:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay... {\alpha&HFF&}but Ryuuzaki... ever since my imprisonment, criminals have stopped dying...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.68,0:01:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay... but Ryuuzaki... {\alpha&HFF&}ever since my imprisonment, criminals have stopped dying...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.84,0:01:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay... but Ryuuzaki... ever since my imprisonment, {\alpha&HFF&}criminals have stopped dying...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.51,0:01:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay... but Ryuuzaki... ever since my imprisonment, criminals have stopped dying...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.80,0:01:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's a good chance that Kira or someone knows about my current predicament, it might be worth investigating alo--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.67,0:01:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.36,0:01:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason they've stopped dying is because you are Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.73,0:01:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.79,0:01:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.91,0:01:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times do I have to tell you this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.49,0:01:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're Kira you would know that criminals are being killed, {\alpha&HFF&}yet I can't see this in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.97,0:01:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're Kira you would know that criminals are being killed, yet I can't see this in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.11,0:01:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki is pretty harsh. {\alpha&HFF&}I can't believe he's not told Light-kun that criminals are still being murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.13,0:01:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki is pretty harsh. I can't believe he's not told Light-kun that criminals are still being murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.69,0:01:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amane.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.90,0:01:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.03,0:01:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't look so good. Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.75,0:01:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Are you stupid or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.83,0:01:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Misa was fine after so many weeks of this, she'd be some kind of weirdo...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.99,0:01:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.16,0:02:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and release me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.36,0:02:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see Light... {\alpha&HFF&}Light... Light... Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.53,0:02:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see Light... Light... {\alpha&HFF&}Light... Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.23,0:02:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see Light... Light... Light... {\alpha&HFF&}Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.00,0:02:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see Light... Light... Light... Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.92,0:02:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like all three of them are reaching their limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.92,0:02:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki, why do you continue to detain Light-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.22,0:02:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should release him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.32,0:02:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That way the Chief will be free as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.78,0:02:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite neither Amane nor Light-kun receiving information about them, criminals continue to be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.49,0:02:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't this tell you enough?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.35,0:02:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.71,0:02:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing I've been able to establish is Amane's extraordinary love for Yagami Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.98,0:02:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki... sorry, but personally,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.41,0:02:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're only doing this because you don't want to accept that your "Light-kun is Kira" theory is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you do think that after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.20,0:02:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's as Light-kun said. Kira killed Lind L. Tailor and those FBI agents.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.88,0:02:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they were able to kill without the need to acquire information, there would have been no need to kill Tailor or the FBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.94,0:02:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much they were investigated, they would never have been caught!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.47,0:03:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Kira does not kill more than it's necessary to."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.52,0:03:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said so yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.59,0:03:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see. {\alpha&HFF&}If they could kill people under those conditions,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.97,0:03:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see. If they could kill people under those conditions,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.00,0:03:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they could have left the FBI agents alone because they would pose no threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.33,0:03:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fifty days have already passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.43,0:03:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in carrying on with this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.77,0:03:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead, we should be focusing on capturing the real Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.99,0:03:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.86,0:03:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.34,0:03:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.67,0:03:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could I get you to return to Headquarters?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.67,0:03:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like everyone to hear my verdict on this matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.63,0:03:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you, Yagami-san, as Light-kun's father, to be the first.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.67,0:03:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.02,0:04:19.07,MINOR SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,0)\pos(362,391)\fscx95\bord3}Three days later
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.04,0:04:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never imagined you would be such an old man, Stalker-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.69,0:04:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a stalker, I'm a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.62,0:04:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Detective?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.92,0:04:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.08,0:04:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the beginning, they mentioned something about "suspicion of being the second Kira"!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.29,0:04:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were actually serious about that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.12,0:04:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely not... the police would never tie me up like a maniac.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.15,0:04:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, if you're releasing me, isn't it a little odd to keep my hands and feet cuffed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.01,0:04:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.03,0:05:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.76,0:05:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.97,0:05:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light! I wanted to see you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.59,0:05:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.47,0:05:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Father?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.00,0:05:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! Misa called Light's dad a stalker and lots of other rude things!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.96,0:05:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet you! I'm Amane Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.10,0:05:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going out with Li--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take them away, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.71,0:05:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Hurry up and get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.35,0:05:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this means we're no longer under suspicion and finally free.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.98,0:05:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.45,0:05:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be taking you two to the execution chamber.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I volunteered to escort you to a top-secret execution chamber in an underground facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.15,0:05:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Execution chamber?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.17,0:05:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.69,0:05:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?! Father?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.93,0:05:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're joking, right, dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.49,0:05:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L has concluded that Yagami Light is Kira and Amane Misa is the second Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.63,0:05:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and if we dispose of both of you, the "Kira killings" will end.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.61,0:06:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The "Kira killings" should have stopped already...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.09,0:06:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, they're still taking place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.94,0:06:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still taking place?! {\alpha&HFF&}That's not what they told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.56,0:06:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still taking place?! That's not what they told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.02,0:06:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was most likely an investigative technique L was using in order to get you to confess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.04,0:06:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not the point...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.56,0:06:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L's proposal of killing both of you, thereby stopping the "Kira killings",
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was quickly accepted by all the heads of the United Nations and the Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.56,0:06:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira will be executed in secret, away from the public eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.29,0:06:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-{\alpha&HFF&}That's stupid! Father! I am {\b1}not{\b0} Kira!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.87,0:06:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's stupid! Father! I am {\b1}not{\b0} Kira!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.63,0:06:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you thinking?! He's you own son!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.41,0:06:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't my decision, {\alpha&HFF&}it was L's decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.66,0:06:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't my decision, it was L's decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.89,0:06:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's solved all sorts of impossible problems in the past, and he's yet to be proved wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.61,0:06:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father... {\alpha&HFF&}you're believing L over me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.44,0:06:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father... you're believing L over me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.10,0:06:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L has even said that if the murders don't stop, {\alpha&HFF&}he will take full responsibility for it, and pay with his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.02,0:06:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L has even said that if the murders don't stop, he will take full responsibility for it, and pay with his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.47,0:06:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L, what are you thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.16,0:07:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that given all the evidence acquired up till now, the conclusion seems inevitable... {\alpha&HFF&}but there's been a mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.73,0:07:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that given all the evidence acquired up till now, the conclusion seems inevitable... but there's been a mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.04,0:07:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L, how did he come to such a conclusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.99,0:07:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something wrong here... this isn't like L at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.89,0:07:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Up until now, he's always been able to offer solid proof when he solves a case... {\alpha&HFF&}is he going to end it all just like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.17,0:07:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Up until now, he's always been able to offer solid proof when he solves a case... is he going to end it all just like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.69,0:07:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.06,0:07:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.89,0:07:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you planning to do, bringing us to such a remote area?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.07,0:07:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad! Is it possible that you're planning to release us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.74,0:07:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, {\alpha&HFF&}no matter what we do here, no one will see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.98,0:07:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, no matter what we do here, no one will see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.47,0:07:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I deliberately brought both of you here instead of the execution chamber.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.14,0:07:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light... {\alpha&HFF&}I'm going to kill you here, and then I'll kill myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.06,0:08:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light... I'm going to kill you here, and then I'll kill myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.73,0:08:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying, father?! Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.23,0:08:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Dad! You're crazy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.69,0:08:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to kill your own child and then yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.77,0:08:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to die, then just die by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you go through with this, then you're no different from Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.34,0:08:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm different from Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.16,0:08:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have responsibilities, both as a parent, and also as the Chief of Police.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.72,0:08:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father, it's exactly as Misa says!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.85,0:08:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we die here, they still won't know the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.73,0:08:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, it's better to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.12,0:08:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.65,0:08:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever path you choose, you will be executed, {\alpha&HFF&}and if that's the case, at least it will be by my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.10,0:08:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever path you choose, you will be executed, and if that's the case, at least it will be by my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.87,0:08:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, father! {\alpha&HFF&}I'm not Kira!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.94,0:08:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, father! I'm not Kira!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I die here, it'll be exactly what Kira wants! {\alpha&HFF&}Don't you see that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.37,0:08:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I die here, it'll be exactly what Kira wants! Don't you see that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.84,0:08:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amane, {\alpha&HFF&}my son and I will die here, but I have no reason to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.31,0:08:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amane, my son and I will die here, but I have no reason to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.37,0:08:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The police will probably find this car soon, {\alpha&HFF&}and then you can be executed at the formal execution chamber.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.78,0:08:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The police will probably find this car soon, and then you can be executed at the formal execution chamber.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.23,0:09:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light... {\alpha&HFF&}we're both murderers; see you in hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.52,0:09:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light... we're both murderers; see you in hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.62,0:09:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.65,0:09:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!!
Comment: 0,0:09:13.98,0:09:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EYECATCHERS
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.50,0:09:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light... {\alpha&HFF&}we're both murderers; see you in hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.11,0:09:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light... we're both murderers; see you in hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.68,0:09:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.70,0:09:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a blank?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.53,0:09:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank god...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.82,0:09:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "Thank god"? {\alpha&HFF&}What are you doing, father?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.93,0:10:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "Thank god"? What are you doing, father?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.84,0:10:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you, forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.09,0:10:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was the sole method of freeing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.55,0:10:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, believe me, I only did this {\b1}because{\b0} I truly believe that you are not Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.99,0:10:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you watching that, Ryuuzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.59,0:10:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did exactly like you asked, and as you can see, I'm still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.79,0:10:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, {\alpha&HFF&}it was a very realistic performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.80,0:10:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it was a very realistic performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.12,0:10:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Amane was truly the second Kira and could kill purely by looking at someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.71,0:10:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure we can assume she would have killed Yagami-san before he shot Light-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.11,0:10:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if Light-kun was Kira, {\alpha&HFF&}the way I have imagined Kira to be, they would kill even a parent if necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.71,0:10:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if Light-kun was Kira, the way I have imagined Kira to be, they would kill even a parent if necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.14,0:10:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, in Light-kun's case, I can't dismiss the possibility that he may have figured out that it was an act at some point.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.48,0:10:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, as promised, I'll end their imprisonment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.91,0:10:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And also as promised... {\alpha&HFF&}Amane Misa, although you may insist that those tapes are occult videos,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.99,0:10:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And also as promised... Amane Misa, although you may insist that those tapes are occult videos,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.14,0:10:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,due to your confession that you sent them, and other points of evidence,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.82,0:11:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you will remain under surveillance until Kira is caught, and everything is resolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.66,0:11:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with that? Are you still suspicious of me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.32,0:11:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you can return to your everyday life. Isn't that enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.75,0:11:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you're innocent, all surveillance means, is that you'll be protected by the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.24,0:11:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really? {\alpha&HFF&}Well, since Misa isn't the second Kira, she just has to think of it as having a bodyguard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.54,0:11:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really? Well, since Misa isn't the second Kira, she just has to think of it as having a bodyguard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.46,0:11:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, Light-kun, as promised, {\alpha&HFF&}I'm prepared to make a pact with you;
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.41,0:11:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, Light-kun, as promised, I'm prepared to make a pact with you;
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.12,0:11:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that is, you'll be with me 24/7 assisting me with this investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.39,0:11:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand, Ryuuzaki. {\alpha&HFF&}Together we'll catch Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.92,0:11:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand, Ryuuzaki. Together we'll catch Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.76,0:11:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'll be counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.99,0:11:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really necessary to go this far, Ryuuzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.73,0:11:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I'm not doing this because I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.48,0:11:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? This is what you meant by being with each other 24/7?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.88,0:12:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're both guys, it's kinda creepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.02,0:12:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you lean that way, Ryuuzaki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.52,0:12:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, I said I'm not doing this because I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.58,0:12:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Light is Misa's Light after all, and if you're around 24 hours a day, when is Misa supposed to go on dates?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.06,0:12:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unavoidably, when you go on a date, it'll be the three of us together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.39,0:12:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Does that mean we have to kiss and stuff in front of you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.68,0:12:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't say you had to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.56,0:12:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I will have to maintain surveillance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.43,0:12:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that?! You're a pervert after all!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.65,0:12:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun, please get Misa-san to shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.66,0:12:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa, stop being selfish over this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.83,0:12:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Given that they can prove you sent those tapes in, {\alpha&HFF&}you should be thankful for being released.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.15,0:12:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Given that they can prove you sent those tapes in, you should be thankful for being released.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.45,0:12:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Even you are saying this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.76,0:12:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa is your girlfriend! Don't you believe in your own girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.55,0:12:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You say that you're my girlfriend... {\alpha&HFF&}but you've just been chasing me around saying that you fell in love with me at first sight...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.97,0:12:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You say that you're my girlfriend... but you've just been chasing me around saying that you fell in love with me at first sight...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.74,0:12:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, when I said, "I love you", you just took advantage of that to kiss me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.90,0:12:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jerk! {\alpha&HFF&}Jerk! Jerk! Je-erk!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.31,0:12:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jerk! Jerk! {\alpha&HFF&}Jerk! Je-erk!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.60,0:12:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jerk! Jerk! Jerk! {\alpha&HFF&}Je-erk!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:12:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jerk! Jerk! Jerk! Je-erk!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.77,0:12:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regarding you "falling in love at first sight", {\alpha&HFF&}that happened on the 22nd of May in Aoyama, right, Misa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.73,0:13:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regarding you "falling in love at first sight", that happened on the 22nd of May in Aoyama, right, Misa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.49,0:13:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.68,0:13:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On that day, why did you go to Aoyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.25,0:13:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What clothes were you wearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.99,0:13:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, I just went on a whim. How many times do you want me to say this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.40,0:13:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I honestly can't remember how I was feeling, or what I was wearing that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.45,0:13:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it that wrong of Misa to hang around Aoyama without a reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.18,0:13:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, when you returned home from Aoyama, you knew Light-kun's name, someone you had just fallen in love with at first sight...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.35,0:13:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.99,0:13:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, you have no idea as to how you knew his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.82,0:13:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.38,0:13:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what if Light-kun is Kira? Then what would you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.39,0:13:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? {\alpha&HFF&}If Light is Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.11,0:13:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? If Light is Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.05,0:13:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.34,0:13:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.21,0:13:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa has always been really grateful to Kira for passing judgement on the murderer that killed Misa's parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.69,0:13:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Light was Kira, I'd love him even more!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.45,0:13:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although, I couldn't possibly love you more than I do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.18,0:13:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're talking about Kira here... {\alpha&HFF&}"I'd love him even more", don't you think that's scary?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.89,0:13:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're talking about Kira here... "I'd love him even more", don't you think that's scary?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.74,0:14:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're talking about if Light was Kira, right? {\alpha&HFF&}That wouldn't be scary at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.73,0:14:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're talking about if Light was Kira, right? That wouldn't be scary at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.58,0:14:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a Kira supporter, so I would try to think up ways to help him, rather than be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.01,0:14:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may get in his way, but I doubt that you'd be able to help him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.58,0:14:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this being the case, it's unmistakable that the second Kira is Misa-san, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.99,0:14:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it seems so obvious. Somehow I don't want to believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.63,0:14:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd be correct not to believe it. 'Cause Misa is not Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.74,0:14:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we'll be placing you under surveillance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.09,0:14:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you want to go out, please contact us in this room by using the private line.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.49,0:14:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've paid your agency so that from now on, whether it's at work or during your own personal time,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.02,0:14:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuda-san can accompany you as your manager, Manager Matsui, at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.02,0:14:46.44,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, I'm Matsui. {\alpha&HFF&}Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.90,0:14:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The police have yet to be informed, so please ensure that you don't reveal this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.44,0:14:48.46,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, I'm Matsui. Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.04,0:14:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want this old man as my manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.64,0:14:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! What's so unsatisfactory about me, Misa-Misa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.12,0:14:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk of homos? {\alpha&HFF&}Dates? Kisses? "Misa-Misa"?! Will you all kindly behave yourselves?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.81,0:14:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk of homos? Dates? {\alpha&HFF&}Kisses? "Misa-Misa"?! Will you all kindly behave yourselves?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.25,0:14:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk of homos? Dates? Kisses? {\alpha&HFF&}"Misa-Misa"?! Will you all kindly behave yourselves?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.74,0:15:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk of homos? Dates? Kisses? "Misa-Misa"?! {\alpha&HFF&}Will you all kindly behave yourselves?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.52,0:15:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk of homos? Dates? Kisses? "Misa-Misa"?! Will you all kindly behave yourselves?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.91,0:15:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is about the Kira investigation! {\alpha&HFF&}Will you take it seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.38,0:15:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is about the Kira investigation! Will you take it seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.35,0:15:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-{\alpha&HFF&}Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.07,0:15:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.66,0:15:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... {\alpha&HFF&}I'm sorry, I know you're taking this seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.64,0:15:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I'm sorry, {\alpha&HFF&}I know you're taking this seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I'm sorry, I know you're taking this seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.52,0:15:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Amane, go to your own room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.09,0:15:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aaww...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.80,0:15:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you "aaww" me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.91,0:15:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light! Even if it's got to be the three of us, let's go on a date, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.32,0:15:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun, are you serious about Amane?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.75,0:15:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Erm, no. It's like I said before, it's kind of one-sided...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.98,0:15:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, could you please act as if you're serious about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.26,0:15:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Given the incident with the video tapes, it's clear that she has some sort of connection with the second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.17,0:15:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, it's clear that she loves you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.61,0:15:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling me to get close to her so that we can find out about the second Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.06,0:15:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. {\alpha&HFF&}I think you would be able to manage that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.04,0:15:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I think you would be able to manage that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.36,0:15:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having you draw out the beginnings of an answer from Amane, was one of the main reasons I released both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.88,0:15:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki... {\alpha&HFF&}even if it's for the sake of solving the Kira investigation,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.42,0:16:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki... even if it's for the sake of solving the Kira investigation,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.85,0:16:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's no way I can bring myself to use a girl's emotions like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.49,0:16:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but please to try understand this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.43,0:16:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For me, walking all over someone's goodwill is one of the worst things you can ever do, it's something that I can't forgive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.93,0:16:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's definitely something strange going on... {\alpha&HFF&}I can only imagine that somehow, his personality changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.04,0:16:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's definitely something strange going on... I can only imagine that somehow, his personality changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.53,0:16:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it even possible to just act like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.07,0:16:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can only assume that not only was Amane Misa being manipulated by Kira, {\alpha&HFF&}but so was Yagami Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.60,0:16:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can only assume that not only was Amane Misa being manipulated by Kira, but so was Yagami Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.92,0:16:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Ryuuzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.25,0:16:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing. You're right, Light-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.89,0:16:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, it'd help me a lot if you could ensure that she doesn't reveal anything about this investigation, given its secrecy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.14,0:16:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki, {\alpha&HFF&}is it possible to change this system of moving hotels every few days?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.36,0:16:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki, is it possible to change this system of moving hotels every few days?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.82,0:16:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I've been thinking about doing so since the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.45,0:17:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, from the moment I met Yagami-san and the others, and decided to take this case, I commenced construction.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.27,0:17:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be completed in a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.08,0:17:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.26,0:17:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Twenty-three floors high with two basement levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.32,0:17:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's constructed in such a way that you can't observe the roof from the outside, and there are two helicopters housed within it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.91,0:17:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.55,0:17:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As much as possible, I'd like everyone to live here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.49,0:17:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we choose to increase the number of people on the investigation, it can accommodate at least 60.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.15,0:17:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely Misa-san won't complain if we give her an entire floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.70,0:17:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, this is amazing! To have gone this far...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.23,0:17:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, Ryuuzaki, where did you get the money for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.07,0:17:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It means that I'll do whatever it takes to solve this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.17,0:17:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't actually answer the question...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.11,0:17:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.99,0:17:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, for being a mass murderer, and for what he's put my father and me through, I can't let Kira get away with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.44,0:17:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do whatever it takes to solve this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.07,0:18:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you'll "do whatever it takes", why don't you get close to Misa-san and try t--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.03,0:18:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not that. That's going against my honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.84,0:18:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so? {\alpha&HFF&}It's a pity...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.34,0:18:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so? It's a pity...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.41,0:18:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing. {\alpha&HFF&}I'm just getting really psyched about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.36,0:18:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing. I'm just getting really psyched about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.91,0:18:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki, {\alpha&HFF&}Yagami-san, Light-kun, let's ensure that we catch Kira, no matter what.
