Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.51,0:18:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki, Yagami-san, Light-kun, let's ensure that we catch Kira, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.52,0:18:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm.. you didn't mention my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.34,0:18:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like everyone is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.51,0:18:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's begin the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.25,0:18:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to further our company's activities and make Yotsuba the greatest enterprise in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.64,0:18:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who do we need to kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.42,0:18:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having someone killed every week is pretty serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.89,0:18:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why has Kira moved from solely passing judgment on criminals to undertaking assassinations?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.19,0:18:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi, don't tell me you have yet to realize it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.59,0:19:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because this will benefit Kira, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.26,0:19:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Benefit Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.74,0:19:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling me that Kira has become an assassin, Higuchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.33,0:19:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were you, I'd shut it more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.46,0:19:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're too stupid, you could get killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.73,0:19:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All eight of us here are still young,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.82,0:19:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's rumored that all of us are capable of going for the company presidency in the near future.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.52,0:19:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In reality, since we started these meetings, out salaries have multiplied to several times the salary of a regular employee.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.35,0:19:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It just seems really strange to me that Kira would give their backing to a single enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.28,0:19:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However I think about it, {\alpha&HFF&}it can only mean that out of the eight of us, one of us is... Kira.
